<item>
            <title>[LU-10018] MDT as a statfs proxy</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-10018</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;given MDT updates statfs data from all OSTs every second it can provide data to the clients. this can be useful for idling connections feature as we won&apos;t need to connect to OST for a single OST_STATFS RPC. this can also make df less expensive in terms of RPC and faster.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
